%8B%E7%8D%B2%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E8%AB%BE%E7%8D%8E | dead-url=no }}</ref>「我對賺錢不感興趣，只要我能的建築能使人開心，我便開心。」<ref name="house">{{cite web| url=http://thehousenews.com/art/建紙板人道房屋-坂茂奪普立茲克獎/| title=建紙板人道房屋 坂茂奪普立茲克獎| publisher=[[主場新聞|主場新聞]]| date=2014-03-25| accessdate=2014-03-25| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606221455/http://thehousenews.com/art/%E5%BB%BA%E7%B4%99%E6%9D%BF%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B-%E5%9D%82%E8%8C%82%E5%A5%AA%E6%99%AE%E7%AB%8B%E8%8C%B2%E5%85%8B%E7%8D%8E/| archivedate=2014-06-06}}</ref>

